{"tid":751861,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"身材勁被要求收埋 糖妹恨飛西班牙開工性感解放","createTime":"2018-07-22T09:02:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T14:20:07.000Z","uid":100136,"like":0,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2421b9df2b3d570e3a90ad9c5b6cc2b1100bc1c3","tid":751861,"uid":100136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T09:02:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180718/_2018071816402783842.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180718%2F_2018071816402783842.jpg&h=238fc116&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n糖妹（黃山怡）以代言人身份現身書展旅遊品牌頒獎禮，為旅遊書擔任了6年代言人的她稱雙方合作，計劃到訪20個地方拍攝，最期待是到西班牙，「如果真係去西班牙，我會性感大解放，解放甚麼暫時賣個關子，總之大家未見過的都有機會露！」<br />\n<br />\n一向密實的糖妹還自爆：「有人嫌我身材太勁呀！話說本月底將為音樂劇開鑼，由於要反串演男仔，被話身材太勁要我收埋，仲話我紮胸都仲有，連我都唔知自己咁勁。」<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180718/_2018071816402725985.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180718%2F_2018071816402725985.jpeg&h=fb608769&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n轉載 : <a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/1269138/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Flife%2Fent%2Frealtime%2F1269138%2F&d=jM4Xazfkj6lOjvklLJQOxb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=ab72047d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Flife%2Fent%2Frealtime%2F1269138%2F&h=cfe88e59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/1269138/</a>"},{"pid":"63f0a2cc4d041ee71fa3dd2f3fef25b0b66ee999","tid":751861,"uid":45332,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T09:03:38.000Z","msg":"黑蚊蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ed4651111236eaacc32b7b5e63ec264dbd6ecf","tid":751861,"uid":2140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T09:03:48.000Z",